{
  "stem": "27509.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But their behavior, when we settled in there, and we had been given-- it was provided for us, because the joint provided funds, and the local committee Kobe of-- there were some Russian Jews who lived in Kobe.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They came from [JAPANESE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they had been doing business in Japan in those days exporting Japanese fine cloth, which in those days they weren't exporting Toyotas and Mazdas in those days.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were exporting textiles, and other such items.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "To-- so they were buying or exporting this stuff to other parts of the world.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So there was a Jewish community with a synagogue, and organization-- organization-- organization-- organization.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they have taken up houses, old houses, and provided mattresses on the floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we had-- we went into already prepared lodgings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We were 11-- in my room, there were 11 people, because the floor took 11 mattresses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So there were 11 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Next to me was lying Henry Korngold, was lying next to me on the floor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we were given one yen and 10 cents per day for food out of this communal thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I think I've told you-- I've mentioned to you the encounter with the banker Szeroszewski, who was standing in front of me in that same queue waiting for that-- for that one yen a day, the man who was the most prominent Jewish banker in Poland, whom-- whom all the old maids-- Jewish maids of Poland entrusted with their dowries that they never used.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That men stood in front of me waiting for the same one yen sustenance to be able to pull through the day, because [INAUDIBLE] whatever he possessed was somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And in the meantime, he came-- he came with nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
